snippet.title: I Expect You To Die 3: Cog In The Machine - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Watch the new trailer for I Expect You To Die 3: Cog In The Machine. Get a peek at what to expect from the upcoming mission in the spy-themed VR puzzle game series, and see what you'll get up to an elite secret agent.

I Expect You To Die 3: Cog In The Machine's new mission arrives in 2023 on Meta Quest 2 and Steam VR.
